n in the 0.6-0.03 Msun mass range and found that it is\nbest reproduced by a log-normal representation with a mean characteristic mass\nof 0.24(+0.01-0.03) Msun, in agreement with earlier studies and the\nextrapolation of the field mass function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2012 08:59:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
