by a non-linear function of the\nspacetime coordinates and define the on-shell form of the potential plus a\nfunctional equation that it has to satisfy. Finally, a general family of (A)dS4\nstatic hairy black holes is explicitly constructed and its properties are\noutlined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2012 13:39:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Apr 2012 21:11:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Apr 2012 15:34:46 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 29 Apr 2012 22:59:57 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 22 May 2012 01:16:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
